java.io.Serializable
public class UnknownErrorException
extends java.lang.Exception

The unknown error exception is thrown when an unknown or unhandled exception was thrown. The error codes -1900 (which indicates that the card itself returned that an error occurred that was unknown for it) and -1901 (which indicates that the PKCS#15 application couldn't be found) are also put in this exception.
